WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:08.000
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:08.000 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 11]

01:17.310 --> 01:18.340
Once I've honed my spirit power

01:18.750 --> 01:19.500
and mastered the technique,

01:20.880 --> 01:22.450
she'll never be hurt by anyone again,

01:23.670 --> 01:24.450
not even me.

01:47.390 --> 01:49.250
Good thing the masters discovered it in time.

01:49.800 --> 01:51.580
That wretch from the Sea Sect

01:52.110 --> 01:53.860
had been hiding among us under a false identity.

01:54.270 --> 01:55.170
She must have been trying to steal

01:55.190 --> 01:56.730
our secret manuals and treasures.

01:58.240 --> 01:59.780
So devious.

02:01.600 --> 02:02.780
Those Sea Sect scoundrels

02:02.800 --> 02:04.450
love practicing these twisted arts.

02:04.910 --> 02:06.420
No wonder she had demonic energy on her.

02:07.160 --> 02:08.810
The masters are too soft.

02:09.030 --> 02:09.940
For someone like that,

02:10.240 --> 02:11.340
we should torture them

02:11.720 --> 02:13.090
to see if they have other schemes.

02:13.760 --> 02:14.650
That female master

02:14.670 --> 02:16.500
taught us technique class for months.

02:16.830 --> 02:17.850
By that logic,

02:18.270 --> 02:19.090
are we all scoundrels

02:19.110 --> 02:20.570
practicing twisted arts too?

02:20.990 --> 02:21.650
Yeah.

02:22.080 --> 02:24.300
Ms. Lin was strict,

02:24.830 --> 02:26.250
but she never harmed any of us.

02:26.870 --> 02:28.020
She taught us well

02:28.390 --> 02:29.810
and even helped us in the last trial.

02:31.760 --> 02:33.370
Since the headmaster hasn't said anything,

02:33.960 --> 02:36.090
some people should drop their prejudice

02:36.110 --> 02:36.810
and stop piling on.

02:37.870 --> 02:38.940
Those not of our kind

02:39.360 --> 02:40.570
are of different mind.

02:40.960 --> 02:43.530
You call those treacherous villains your master?

02:44.670 --> 02:45.180
What,

02:45.710 --> 02:48.620
are you in league with demons too?

02:49.150 --> 02:49.530
You...

02:52.200 --> 02:54.410
I mean, the situation isn't clear yet.

02:54.640 --> 02:55.810
Don't slander good people.

02:56.270 --> 02:57.090
Good people?

02:58.480 --> 02:59.850
When the Sea Calamity struck,

03:00.150 --> 03:01.690
countless cultivators

03:01.710 --> 03:02.810
died fighting demons.

03:03.710 --> 03:05.500
Now the Sea Sect openly wields demonic tools

03:05.520 --> 03:06.340
and forges demonic artifacts.

03:06.670 --> 03:08.780
Anyone who sides with demons can't be good.

03:09.320 --> 03:11.060
Anyone tied to demons

03:11.080 --> 03:12.180
is a villain!

03:16.200 --> 03:16.740
Tongzhou.

03:18.920 --> 03:19.970
Am I right?

03:22.640 --> 03:23.690
When the demons invaded,

03:24.110 --> 03:25.570
the Central Plains sects were nearly wiped out.

03:25.990 --> 03:27.500
Of the elders of Xingzheng Hall,

03:27.520 --> 03:28.370
only two survived.

03:29.590 --> 03:30.850
But the Sea Sect kept a vague stance

03:31.240 --> 03:32.090
and escaped the catastrophe.

03:32.960 --> 03:34.220
They might not be enemies,

03:35.080 --> 03:36.180
but they're not friends either.

03:42.360 --> 03:43.530
Yecha's whereabouts?

03:44.870 --> 03:46.300
Did one of your ancestors

03:46.320 --> 03:47.620
die at Yecha's hands?

03:47.960 --> 03:48.940
Are you seeking revenge?

03:52.870 --> 03:55.220
We just want to know where the Demon Lord is.

03:58.040 --> 04:00.300
He was destroyed five hundred years ago.

04:00.960 --> 04:02.180
If Yecha were still alive,

04:02.550 --> 04:04.250
he wouldn't allow his broken horns

04:04.270 --> 04:05.780
to be used as artifacts of the Sea Sect.

04:08.360 --> 04:09.340
Come to think of it,

04:09.670 --> 04:11.970
you Gaolu people have always had

04:11.990 --> 04:12.970
an ambiguous stance toward demons.

04:13.550 --> 04:15.060
I heard that during the Sea Calamity,

04:15.080 --> 04:16.340
disciples from Gaolu

04:16.360 --> 04:17.970
tried to cross the mountain-sea barrier.

04:18.760 --> 04:19.500
Could you

04:20.320 --> 04:21.890
have some connection to demons?

04:27.710 --> 04:28.860
Since it's an ancestral charge,

04:29.080 --> 04:31.300
the Divine Lord's soul probably won't dissipate so easily.

04:33.640 --> 04:34.690
We'll keep searching.

04:36.830 --> 04:37.330
Who's there?

04:42.960 --> 04:43.500
Gelin?

04:51.000 --> 04:52.810
I looked for you for practice, but couldn't find you.

04:53.440 --> 04:54.130
Turns out Ye...

04:54.150 --> 04:55.540
Turns out you two were here.

04:57.590 --> 04:59.210
Didn't we say that the three of us stick together?

04:59.960 --> 05:01.570
Why do you always leave me out?

05:05.390 --> 05:06.690
We didn't mean to.

05:07.320 --> 05:08.450
It's just that there are things...

05:12.270 --> 05:13.810
we haven't figured out ourselves.

05:14.030 --> 05:14.860
We didn't want to worry you.

05:17.880 --> 05:19.980
I didn't mean to pry into your secrets.

05:22.230 --> 05:23.570
I was just... worried about you.

05:24.590 --> 05:25.130
Gelin,

05:25.830 --> 05:26.540
it's my fault.

05:26.910 --> 05:28.060
We're family.

05:28.790 --> 05:30.100
Family can't be wrong.

05:38.470 --> 05:39.250
What's that?

05:47.390 --> 05:48.130
Mr. Zuo Qiu,

05:48.790 --> 05:50.100
Jiao acted recklessly

05:50.120 --> 05:51.300
and caused trouble at the academy.

05:51.910 --> 05:53.540
It's my fault for not keeping my daughter in check.

05:54.470 --> 05:55.210
Mr. Shen,

05:55.830 --> 05:57.010
I was weak before.

05:57.350 --> 05:58.740
I was afraid I couldn't protect her.

05:59.440 --> 06:00.450
Now I've come to realize

06:01.120 --> 06:02.100
that hesitation

06:02.120 --> 06:03.060
and indecision

06:03.080 --> 06:04.330
hurt the most.

06:11.030 --> 06:12.180
[Mr. Shen, Wanxian Sect]
I'll follow my heart

06:12.470 --> 06:13.740
and go to the East Sea with Jiao.

06:14.590 --> 06:17.130
I'll spend the rest of my life protecting her.

06:19.150 --> 06:19.810
Yanfan.

06:24.960 --> 06:25.660
Mr. Zuo Qiu,

06:27.080 --> 06:28.210
what is this all about?

06:30.520 --> 06:32.010
The division between the Mountain and Sea Sects

06:32.440 --> 06:34.130
is just human prejudice.

06:35.120 --> 06:37.660
If someone has the courage to break through those barriers,

06:39.000 --> 06:41.180
it can be a beautiful thing.

06:46.470 --> 06:47.940
Isn't Jiao a wretch from the Sea Sect?

06:48.120 --> 06:49.620
Why would Mr. Mo be with her?

06:49.640 --> 06:50.740
Mr. Mo is really leaving?

06:51.270 --> 06:52.690
Then who's going to teach us artifact crafting?

06:53.270 --> 06:54.620
Bu said

06:55.000 --> 06:55.980
the Sea Calamity is coming,

06:56.000 --> 06:57.570
and the Mountain and Sea Sects

06:57.590 --> 06:58.420
must unite against it.

06:58.520 --> 06:59.330
He also said

06:59.350 --> 07:00.210
that when we graduate,

07:00.230 --> 07:01.420
people from the East Sea will be here to recruit.

07:01.680 --> 07:02.890
Maybe we'll see him again then.

07:03.080 --> 07:03.940
Mee at the East Sea?

07:04.960 --> 07:05.940
Nonsense!

07:06.200 --> 07:07.450
How could we possibly join forces?

07:07.880 --> 07:09.570
Mr. Mo was a top disciple of Xingzheng Hall.

07:09.590 --> 07:10.940
He would never side with a wretch.

07:11.080 --> 07:12.740
She must have bewitched him.

07:13.150 --> 07:13.570
Tongzhou,

07:13.710 --> 07:14.690
let's tell Mr. Xuanshan

07:14.710 --> 07:15.740
about this.

07:16.200 --> 07:17.620
He already knows.

07:18.230 --> 07:19.370
- Then what did he say...?
- I've failed Master.

07:22.760 --> 07:23.540
From today on,

07:24.230 --> 07:25.570
I am no longer a disciple of Xingzheng Hall.

07:29.350 --> 07:30.540
You two really made up?

07:31.790 --> 07:33.210
I'm going to the East Sea with Jiao.

07:34.030 --> 07:36.100
I don't know when I'll see you all again.

07:38.200 --> 07:39.010
Before I go,

07:39.470 --> 07:40.890
let me break your Fragrance Bond.

07:47.440 --> 07:48.420
You want to break the Fragrance Bond?

07:49.560 --> 07:53.250
♪The warmth within my arms♪

07:53.630 --> 07:54.520
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

07:54.520 --> 07:55.450
We're parting ways anyway.

07:56.350 --> 07:57.180
It's useless now.

07:58.270 --> 07:59.060
Might as well break it.

07:59.060 --> 08:00.370
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

08:00.730 --> 08:04.000
♪Keep you warm until sunrise?♪

08:04.370 --> 08:07.570
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

08:07.890 --> 08:11.090
♪I can no longer tell you♪

08:12.390 --> 08:13.180
Please, Mr. Mo.

08:13.180 --> 08:14.690
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

08:14.970 --> 08:18.010
♪Utter that line♪

08:18.270 --> 08:19.950
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

08:20.310 --> 08:24.230
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

08:25.590 --> 08:27.230
♪You're still screaming♪

08:27.510 --> 08:31.830
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

08:32.270 --> 08:36.510
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stand in its way♪

08:36.870 --> 08:39.710
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

08:40.030 --> 08:46.520
♪Leaping straight into that heartbreaking past♪

08:46.880 --> 08:51.000
♪Just to keep you safe♪

09:02.320 --> 09:06.080
♪My breath is about to stop♪

09:06.280 --> 09:09.600
♪Those hands can no longer hold yours♪

09:10.080 --> 09:13.080
♪Through the future snow, wind, and fog♪

09:13.320 --> 09:16.280
♪Who will be there by your side?♪

09:16.400 --> 09:20.080
♪I smile as it ends♪

09:20.520 --> 09:23.800
♪Afraid that you might cry for me♪

09:24.280 --> 09:27.360
♪Quietly, I turn into a sky lantern♪

09:27.680 --> 09:30.600
♪To light your way through the night♪

09:31.070 --> 09:32.750
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

09:33.110 --> 09:37.030
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

09:38.390 --> 09:40.030
♪You're still screaming♪

09:40.310 --> 09:42.040
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

09:42.040 --> 09:42.660
What's wrong?

09:45.110 --> 09:45.730
Strange.

09:46.990 --> 09:47.690
It won't break.

09:49.440 --> 09:50.260
Unresolved attachments

09:50.750 --> 09:51.540
make the bond unbreakable.

09:52.470 --> 09:54.380
You three share deep feelings for each other.

09:55.390 --> 10:00.040
♪To lay all your days in peace♪

10:00.040 --> 10:01.950
♪Who says that love and hate♪

10:02.270 --> 10:04.680
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped?♪

10:04.680 --> 10:05.970
You just won't give up, will you?

10:07.310 --> 10:09.190
♪I will level the seas and mountains♪

10:10.630 --> 10:11.260
Forget it.

10:11.260 --> 10:13.790
♪Break the waves, no matter how mad it seems♪

10:14.110 --> 10:18.470
♪The storm looms, yet I stand in its way♪

10:19.750 --> 10:21.140
If the feelings were only one-sided,

10:21.160 --> 10:22.060
it would break.

10:23.350 --> 10:23.970
Since it won't,

10:24.470 --> 10:25.690
it only shows the three of you

10:25.990 --> 10:27.180
truly care for each other.

10:28.350 --> 10:31.330
Young people always fail to see their true feelings.

10:52.870 --> 10:53.540
Ye, hello.

11:12.230 --> 11:12.570
Gelin.

11:12.590 --> 11:14.090
I... I have things to do.

11:14.750 --> 11:15.540
I'm leaving.

11:20.200 --> 11:21.970
Time flies.

11:23.080 --> 11:23.660
Lifei,

11:24.040 --> 11:25.060
you said you wanted to join Wuyue Court.

11:25.080 --> 11:25.900
Are you confident?

11:28.830 --> 11:31.420
Wuyue Court is the number one immortal sect in the world.

11:31.990 --> 11:33.730
Some people have average talent

11:34.280 --> 11:36.330
and can't even use their spirit power properly,

11:37.200 --> 11:39.780
yet they still dream of getting into Wuyue Court?

11:42.510 --> 11:44.810
At least we'll try with our own abilities.

11:45.710 --> 11:46.850
Unlike some people

11:47.590 --> 11:48.610
who rely on connections.

11:49.510 --> 11:50.450
Connections?

11:51.040 --> 11:52.690
We are of imperial blood.

11:53.040 --> 11:54.300
We belong in Xingzheng Hall.

11:55.080 --> 11:55.940
As for you,

11:56.630 --> 11:58.210
Gaolu offended Longming Sanctuary.

11:58.710 --> 12:00.090
Which sect do you think

12:00.280 --> 12:01.300
would still accept you?

12:01.560 --> 12:02.020
You...

12:02.350 --> 12:02.940
Lanya.

12:03.920 --> 12:06.020
What, did I say something wrong?

12:10.200 --> 12:12.420
Not every cultivation sect fears Longming Sanctuary.

12:13.110 --> 12:14.490
And not every cultivator

12:14.510 --> 12:15.780
is a bootlicker.

12:25.040 --> 12:27.810
I heard there's a new sect in Xizhou called Dizang Sect.

12:28.350 --> 12:29.420
They specialize in stealth

12:29.440 --> 12:30.180
and transformation.

12:30.680 --> 12:32.210
They've taken in many people from Gaolu.

12:36.750 --> 12:37.260
Xiuyuan,

12:37.830 --> 12:38.610
where do you plan to go?

13:01.870 --> 13:02.730
I'm going back to study.

13:08.870 --> 13:09.300
Lifei!

13:09.750 --> 13:10.300
Lifei.

13:11.110 --> 13:11.540
Lifei.

13:15.400 --> 13:16.380
Take this.

13:17.400 --> 13:18.090
What is it?

13:21.080 --> 13:22.730
Sanctuary of Dragons and Phoenixes?

13:24.590 --> 13:25.850
What dragon and phoenix?

13:25.990 --> 13:26.780
Is this some imperial token?

13:26.920 --> 13:27.900
With this, you'll have

13:28.280 --> 13:29.490
the same authority as me in the Yue State.

13:29.710 --> 13:30.970
It'll make things easier for you.

13:31.320 --> 13:33.140
Why would I go to Yue?

13:34.200 --> 13:34.780
Lifei,

13:35.230 --> 13:36.140
you're going to Wuyue Court

13:36.280 --> 13:37.610
to find your master, right?

13:37.870 --> 13:38.660
But you don't have to

13:38.870 --> 13:40.180
go to Wuyue Court for him yourself.

13:40.470 --> 13:41.300
I can help you look for him.

13:41.750 --> 13:42.940
Wait for my news in Yue.

13:43.230 --> 13:44.020
His Majesty

13:44.280 --> 13:45.420
is kind and warm-hearted.

13:45.800 --> 13:47.180
You can eat or do whatever

13:47.510 --> 13:47.970
you want there.

13:49.080 --> 13:50.140
This is too valuable.

13:50.280 --> 13:51.090
I can't accept it.

13:52.440 --> 13:53.210
Why?

13:53.230 --> 13:53.780
Take it.

13:54.590 --> 13:56.260
Finding my master is my own business.

13:56.470 --> 13:57.660
I can't let someone else do it for me.

13:59.230 --> 13:59.900
Take it back.

14:04.080 --> 14:04.780
Lifei.

14:05.080 --> 14:06.300
After I find my master,

14:06.960 --> 14:08.380
I'll go back to Qingqiu with him.

14:08.710 --> 14:10.260
Besides, you have your own missions.

14:10.680 --> 14:11.690
You need to go to Xingzheng Hall

14:11.920 --> 14:13.780
and win over all those

14:13.800 --> 14:15.300
who oppose you.

14:15.920 --> 14:16.970
You need to make Yue

14:16.990 --> 14:17.850
and Xingzheng Hall prosper.

14:18.110 --> 14:19.140
But for you, I would...

14:19.160 --> 14:20.090
I don't want that.

14:25.870 --> 14:26.570
Tongzhou,

14:27.080 --> 14:27.940
you're a prince.

14:28.590 --> 14:30.540
You carry so many burdens and expectations.

14:31.110 --> 14:32.020
But I'm different.

14:33.080 --> 14:35.060
I just want to live an ordinary life with my master.

14:35.510 --> 14:36.490
Just food on the table,

14:37.080 --> 14:38.060
and a peaceful end.

14:38.830 --> 14:40.330
We're not meant to walk the same path.

14:41.750 --> 14:42.660
You're not willing now.

14:43.510 --> 14:44.140
What about later?

14:44.750 --> 14:45.850
What if you change your mind someday...

14:45.960 --> 14:46.610
Later?

14:47.440 --> 14:48.900
When you go to Xingzheng Hall,

14:48.920 --> 14:50.730
princesses and fairies will flock around you.

14:51.080 --> 14:52.260
You'll be so happy

14:52.280 --> 14:53.140
that you'll forget all about me.

14:57.230 --> 14:58.060
With the Fragrance Bond as witness

14:59.080 --> 14:59.940
and Chufeng Academy as proof,

15:00.830 --> 15:01.810
I will never forget you.

15:05.200 --> 15:07.260
It's just a childhood game.

15:07.830 --> 15:09.300
Not worth remembering for a lifetime.

15:15.200 --> 15:15.810
Prince Ying,

15:17.160 --> 15:18.060
when Xingzheng Hall becomes

15:18.080 --> 15:19.610
the number one immortal sect,

15:20.280 --> 15:23.060
I'll come to you for a toast,

15:23.710 --> 15:24.900
wishing you a bright future

15:25.200 --> 15:26.210
and eternal glory.

15:36.590 --> 15:37.180
Tongzhou.

15:37.800 --> 15:39.780
That token is meant for your future wife.

15:40.040 --> 15:41.450
Why did you give it to Jiang Lifei?

15:42.680 --> 15:43.610
Because I like her.

15:45.350 --> 15:46.380
You like her?

15:47.160 --> 15:48.450
What do you even see in her?

15:48.870 --> 15:50.810
She has no background, and no skills.

15:50.920 --> 15:51.610
She's rude.

15:51.960 --> 15:52.900
And she's greedy for money!

15:54.830 --> 15:55.660
Lanya,

15:56.040 --> 15:57.540
she's really different from anyone else.

15:58.630 --> 16:00.060
I've never wanted to be with someone

16:00.080 --> 16:01.450
so badly before.

16:02.560 --> 16:03.330
Tongzhou,

16:03.960 --> 16:05.810
His Majesty already approved our engagement.

16:05.920 --> 16:07.660
Aren't you supposed to marry me?

16:08.710 --> 16:09.420
Besides,

16:09.680 --> 16:11.020
what's the point of thinking about her?

16:11.320 --> 16:12.610
She doesn't think about you at all!

16:14.990 --> 16:15.690
I see.

16:17.510 --> 16:18.450
She must have used

16:18.470 --> 16:19.780
some cheap trick on you.

16:19.920 --> 16:21.210
She put a mind-control spell on you, right?

16:21.400 --> 16:22.060
Where is it? Where?

16:22.080 --> 16:22.610
Lanya.

16:23.470 --> 16:24.090
Sit down.

16:27.440 --> 16:28.210
Tongzhou,

16:28.440 --> 16:29.610
think carefully.

16:30.320 --> 16:31.900
We've known each other for over ten years.

16:32.200 --> 16:33.900
You've known her for...

16:34.560 --> 16:36.260
less than a year!

16:37.920 --> 16:38.610
Alright.

16:39.510 --> 16:40.850
Let's focus on the graduation exam first.

16:42.200 --> 16:43.060
I'm done preparing!

16:43.710 --> 16:44.900
If I can't marry you,

16:45.080 --> 16:45.780
why bother taking the exam?

16:46.750 --> 16:47.420
I'm not taking it!

16:59.160 --> 17:00.380
Everyone, run!

17:01.350 --> 17:02.450
Everyone, run!

17:03.510 --> 17:05.210
Everyone, run!

17:06.110 --> 17:07.450
What's that sound?

17:14.510 --> 17:15.420
It's Gugu Chicken.

17:15.640 --> 17:16.660
Gugu Chicken is warning us.

17:18.070 --> 17:18.940
It says...

17:19.310 --> 17:21.420
Everyone, run!

17:21.710 --> 17:22.580
Everyone, run!

17:24.600 --> 17:25.940
Why is there miasma in the academy?

17:26.470 --> 17:27.730
There's demonic energy!

17:30.920 --> 17:32.620
No, it's demonic energy!

17:32.840 --> 17:33.420
Demonic energy?

17:33.640 --> 17:34.490
Hurry!

17:34.510 --> 17:35.530
Everyone head to Hongyang Hall!

17:56.710 --> 17:58.340
Go find the masters!

18:44.270 --> 18:44.820
Bu.

18:58.400 --> 18:59.050
Bu!

18:59.400 --> 18:59.860
Don't move!

19:09.270 --> 19:09.690
Tongzhou,

19:09.920 --> 19:10.450
light the way.

19:31.880 --> 19:32.380
Let's go.

19:42.470 --> 19:42.970
Watch out!

19:51.270 --> 19:51.730
Lifei!

19:52.710 --> 19:53.340
Are you okay?

20:03.030 --> 20:04.530
Where did this demonic fog come from?

20:07.160 --> 20:09.490
Could the demons have invaded?

20:09.920 --> 20:11.100
Were the masters all killed?

20:12.360 --> 20:13.290
We can't count on the masters.

20:13.680 --> 20:14.420
We need to leave now.

20:15.360 --> 20:17.100
Baishan Hall hasn't been corrupted by demonic energy yet.

20:17.600 --> 20:18.340
Our artifacts are failing.

20:18.360 --> 20:19.010
Can't fly on our swords.

20:19.600 --> 20:20.290
How do we get there?

20:41.230 --> 20:42.420
We don't know what happened

20:42.750 --> 20:44.140
to Mr. Zuo and the other masters.

20:47.360 --> 20:47.940
Lifei.

20:49.270 --> 20:50.660
How did you summon the rainbow deer?

20:52.270 --> 20:54.250
I saw Ms. Mu do it before.

20:54.270 --> 20:55.340
It's called the spirit-summoning spell.

20:55.360 --> 20:57.010
Anything with spirit should be able to hear it.

20:57.600 --> 20:58.210
I never expected

20:58.230 --> 20:59.530
that only it remains here.

21:04.750 --> 21:05.420
Tongzhou!

21:48.840 --> 21:50.050
Who set up this barrier here?

21:54.160 --> 21:54.900
By this talisman,

21:54.990 --> 21:55.690
evil spirits reveal themselves.

21:55.990 --> 21:56.290
Go!

22:07.040 --> 22:08.310
[Xiangxiang]

22:08.310 --> 22:09.050
What kind of creature is this?

22:09.070 --> 22:09.820
Don't hurt her!

22:13.600 --> 22:13.970
Here.

22:15.440 --> 22:16.860
She's Mr. Hu's spiritual pet, Xiangxiang.

22:18.510 --> 22:19.140
Spiritual pet?

22:19.920 --> 22:22.450
Looks more like a nasty monster to me.

22:23.030 --> 22:24.180
Monsters aren't necessarily worse than humans.

22:24.710 --> 22:25.730
Some ungrateful people

22:25.960 --> 22:27.010
are far worse.

22:27.640 --> 22:28.210
Oh really?

22:28.550 --> 22:29.380
How so?

22:29.880 --> 22:30.530
You there.

22:31.070 --> 22:32.290
Lifei was reaching for you.

22:32.310 --> 22:33.050
Why did you push her?

22:33.750 --> 22:34.450
I pushed her?

22:35.400 --> 22:36.250
Why don't you say

22:36.400 --> 22:37.660
she just lost her footing?

22:43.840 --> 22:44.730
Xiangxiang, don't be scared.

22:45.200 --> 22:46.450
We're Mr. Hu's disciples.

22:46.790 --> 22:47.660
We won't hurt you.

22:48.790 --> 22:49.860
Tell us,

22:50.710 --> 22:52.660
did you set up this barrier?

22:54.600 --> 22:55.860
How did you know

22:55.880 --> 22:56.860
it could block demonic energy?

22:57.710 --> 22:59.770
I heard it from Mr. Hu.

23:00.270 --> 23:02.620
He told me to set up this formation

23:02.920 --> 23:04.380
if danger comes.

23:04.750 --> 23:05.940
What else did Mr. Hu say?

23:06.470 --> 23:07.490
He said

23:07.920 --> 23:09.900
there's a sword-forging terrace to the southeast.

23:10.510 --> 23:12.290
It contains the Sunflare Fire

23:12.920 --> 23:16.250
that can burn away all evil things.

23:22.360 --> 23:23.530
I've heard of the Sunflare Fire.

23:24.510 --> 23:25.420
It can incinerate demonic energy.

23:30.710 --> 23:32.420
The sword-forging terrace is the farthest from Baishan Peak.

23:33.640 --> 23:35.580
And the path there is covered in demonic fog.

23:39.270 --> 23:39.900
Tongzhou,

23:40.270 --> 23:41.860
news of the academy being attacked

23:41.880 --> 23:42.690
will spread.

23:43.360 --> 23:43.820
His Majesty

23:44.160 --> 23:45.100
will probably

23:45.120 --> 23:46.210
send someone for us soon.

23:46.840 --> 23:48.690
We should stay here

23:48.990 --> 23:49.690
and not act rashly.

23:54.400 --> 23:56.450
But my power is too weak.

23:57.230 --> 24:00.490
This barrier can only hold for two hours.

24:07.880 --> 24:08.690
I'll go with you.

24:09.600 --> 24:10.730
Let's go find the Sunflare Fire.

24:11.120 --> 24:12.290
You must stay here

24:12.470 --> 24:13.140
and wait for rescue.

25:39.840 --> 25:40.660
If we can't work together,

25:41.160 --> 25:42.010
we'll never make it out.

25:45.440 --> 25:46.140
Let's cooperate

25:46.550 --> 25:47.420
and get through this first.

26:02.270 --> 26:03.010
The sword-forging terrace!

26:30.960 --> 26:31.580
The Sunflare

26:32.120 --> 26:33.050
has died out?

26:42.070 --> 26:43.050
The defensive formation is about to fail.

26:43.270 --> 26:43.730
Hurry!

26:45.400 --> 26:45.900
Tongzhou,

26:46.310 --> 26:47.140
think about

26:47.640 --> 26:48.770
where you heard about the Sunflare.

26:49.120 --> 26:50.140
How do we ignite it?

26:51.160 --> 26:54.180
Once, Bu had us study in the library.

26:55.270 --> 26:56.820
I found a book in the attic.

26:57.710 --> 26:58.620
It said

26:58.880 --> 27:00.180
the Sunflare is a spiritual flame.

27:00.680 --> 27:03.620
It requires several people to channel their spirit power together

27:03.920 --> 27:04.730
in unison

27:04.990 --> 27:05.730
to ignite it.

27:14.990 --> 27:15.660
Let's begin.

27:51.550 --> 27:52.050
The Sunflare

27:53.230 --> 27:53.860
ignited?

27:57.470 --> 27:58.490
Why is it dying again?

27:59.920 --> 28:00.660
The demonic energy is too thick.

28:01.030 --> 28:01.690
It won't catch.

28:25.160 --> 28:25.820
Demonic energy is drawn to blood.

28:26.550 --> 28:27.250
Once it smells blood,

28:27.790 --> 28:28.580
it will be drawn away.

28:29.790 --> 28:30.340
No!

28:38.880 --> 28:39.490
Lifei,

28:40.230 --> 28:41.050
live well.

28:44.440 --> 28:45.100
Get into Wuyue Court.

28:45.360 --> 28:46.140
Find your master.

28:50.470 --> 28:51.010
Xiuyuan.

28:57.230 --> 28:57.730
Xiuyuan!

29:10.230 --> 29:10.620
Lifei,

29:11.070 --> 29:12.530
don't lose focus. Hold on.

29:44.310 --> 29:44.900
It's done.

29:52.270 --> 29:52.730
Lifei!

29:59.310 --> 30:00.010
Lei Xiuyuan.

30:01.440 --> 30:02.180
Xiuyuan.

30:03.070 --> 30:03.940
Wake up.

30:04.120 --> 30:04.940
Don't die.

30:05.990 --> 30:07.530
I don't want to owe you again.

30:08.230 --> 30:09.050
Lei Xiuyuan!

30:09.460 --> 30:11.960
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

30:12.270 --> 30:12.860
Xiuyuan.

30:12.860 --> 30:14.400
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

30:14.400 --> 30:15.180
Wake up.

30:16.510 --> 30:17.820
Wake up now!

30:19.220 --> 30:22.700
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

30:23.420 --> 30:25.780
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

30:26.380 --> 30:27.900
♪No calamity can rival♪

30:28.300 --> 30:31.340
♪The lingering thread of a fragrance♪

30:33.110 --> 30:36.640
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

30:37.310 --> 30:39.680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

30:40.000 --> 30:43.200
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds and break through the waves♪

30:43.800 --> 30:46.080
♪The heart's ocean knows no shore♪

30:46.480 --> 30:50.200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

30:50.840 --> 30:53.240
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

30:53.680 --> 30:56.840
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water♪

30:57.440 --> 30:59.800
♪And falling petals♪

31:00.520 --> 31:04.790
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪

31:15.160 --> 31:15.900
Congratulations!

31:16.230 --> 31:17.140
You've passed the trial!

31:22.840 --> 31:23.580
Trial?

31:27.360 --> 31:30.050
You will become the rising young elites

31:30.360 --> 31:32.210
of the immortal sects.

31:32.680 --> 31:33.730
With great cultivation

31:34.640 --> 31:35.690
comes great responsibility.

31:37.790 --> 31:39.010
When the coming calamity strikes

31:39.440 --> 31:40.580
and all life withers

31:41.030 --> 31:42.450
like kindling in a fire,

31:42.920 --> 31:44.970
you must stand firm as pillars,

31:45.470 --> 31:46.620
for heaven and for the people.

31:46.880 --> 31:49.940
Only by purifying the world with righteousness

31:50.200 --> 31:53.490
can one truly be called a cultivator.

31:59.160 --> 32:01.290
Now that you are about to leave the academy,

32:01.600 --> 32:02.860
those who have found this path

32:03.070 --> 32:04.380
must hold to it

32:04.510 --> 32:05.580
and never betray it.

32:06.310 --> 32:07.290
For those who have not,

32:07.880 --> 32:09.820
I hope you will reflect and act wisely

32:10.750 --> 32:12.730
in the days ahead.

32:29.550 --> 32:30.530
Not bad at all.

32:31.360 --> 32:32.210
Quick reactions.

32:32.710 --> 32:33.450
Fast on your feet.

32:34.880 --> 32:37.690
In times of danger, you set aside your differences

32:38.070 --> 32:39.530
and listened to Xiangxiang.

32:40.990 --> 32:42.010
Especially

32:42.550 --> 32:45.860
Jiang Lifei, Lei Xiuyuan, and Ji Tongzhou.

32:47.120 --> 32:48.420
They risked their lives

32:48.920 --> 32:50.250
for the safety of others.

32:51.710 --> 32:53.580
Though a bit slow to act,

32:54.310 --> 32:56.100
they didn't disgrace the academy.

33:00.360 --> 33:01.250
That said,

33:03.270 --> 33:04.660
there were also those

33:05.120 --> 33:07.940
who abandoned their fellows in crisis.

33:08.710 --> 33:09.420
Zhou Shun.

33:09.990 --> 33:10.900
Dong Jiashuo.

33:11.550 --> 33:12.770
They acted only for themselves.

33:13.270 --> 33:14.180
They will not graduate.

33:14.920 --> 33:18.050
Also, Lanya harbored ill intent

33:18.710 --> 33:19.770
and plotted against her companions.

33:20.790 --> 33:21.730
She will be expelled

33:22.310 --> 33:23.180
and never permitted to return!

33:23.990 --> 33:24.530
Tongzhou...

33:46.990 --> 33:47.490
Yes!

33:48.070 --> 33:49.050
I did go after her!

33:49.600 --> 33:50.530
Because Jiang Lifei

33:50.550 --> 33:52.010
doesn't deserve your favor,

33:52.160 --> 33:53.620
nor does she deserve to enter any immortal sect!

34:02.960 --> 34:03.860
Go back to the Yue State.

34:04.960 --> 34:06.250
Back to Yue?

34:06.790 --> 34:08.180
Shouldn't I be entering Xingzheng Hall?

34:10.270 --> 34:10.860
Tongzhou,

34:11.120 --> 34:12.340
you let Zhao Mingli in.

34:12.440 --> 34:13.490
I can get in too, can't I?

34:13.800 --> 34:15.380
Elder Zhenyun is missing.

34:15.510 --> 34:16.860
And Xingzheng Hall is in turmoil.

34:17.280 --> 34:18.050
Given your temperament,

34:18.320 --> 34:19.860
now may not be the right time for you to join.

34:21.720 --> 34:22.610
You're lying!

34:23.590 --> 34:25.090
That's not how you really feel.

34:25.720 --> 34:26.340
Tongzhou,

34:26.840 --> 34:28.050
you just don't want me to stay.

34:28.400 --> 34:30.010
You're afraid I'll come between you and Jiang Lifei, right?

34:30.590 --> 34:32.300
What's between us has nothing to do with Lifei.

34:35.190 --> 34:36.130
Go back to Yue.

34:36.760 --> 34:37.780
Stay by His Majesty's side.

34:38.030 --> 34:39.300
You can still be the carefree princess

34:39.800 --> 34:41.260
you used to be.

34:46.630 --> 34:47.260
Lanya.

34:49.190 --> 34:49.940
Lanya!

34:55.880 --> 34:56.740
Time really does fly.

34:56.990 --> 34:58.340
In the blink of an eye, we're graduating.

34:58.760 --> 34:59.420
Yeah.

35:00.240 --> 35:02.130
What do you guys think?

35:02.360 --> 35:03.530
The master already asked.

35:04.150 --> 35:05.490
Have you decided

35:06.070 --> 35:06.740
where to go?

35:09.510 --> 35:10.490
What about you?

35:10.920 --> 35:11.780
I

35:11.800 --> 35:13.490
was thinking we could go to the Dizang Sect together.

35:14.030 --> 35:15.170
Even though Gaolu is gone,

35:15.280 --> 35:16.260
as long as we're together,

35:16.510 --> 35:18.010
it's some comfort.

35:19.670 --> 35:21.340
Count me out.

35:24.400 --> 35:25.860
I haven't decided where to go yet.

35:26.760 --> 35:27.970
You're not coming with us?

35:30.440 --> 35:31.650
Before, I was too young.

35:32.030 --> 35:34.260
I just followed you and Ye around.

35:34.920 --> 35:35.970
Now I'm grown.

35:36.760 --> 35:38.050
I want to make a decision for myself this time.

35:39.280 --> 35:40.570
Gelin, we...

35:40.880 --> 35:41.490
Lifei!

35:44.110 --> 35:46.380
I heard Wuyue Court is really hard to get into.

35:46.510 --> 35:48.380
They haven't recruited from here in years.

35:48.880 --> 35:50.490
Who knows what's happening this year.

35:51.840 --> 35:52.610
I'm not worried.

35:54.360 --> 35:55.530
I've got some aces.

35:58.510 --> 35:59.340
What's this?

35:59.800 --> 36:01.130
This is a pendant Qin gave me

36:01.150 --> 36:01.970
when he left.

36:02.320 --> 36:04.450
He told me to come to him at Wuyue Court.

36:04.470 --> 36:05.450
He's nice.

36:06.670 --> 36:07.490
And this one.

36:07.800 --> 36:08.820
This one's even more impressive.

36:09.030 --> 36:10.940
It's from Elder Dongyang of Wuyue Court.

36:12.550 --> 36:15.260
You're full of surprises.

36:16.400 --> 36:17.700
You'll get into Wuyue Court.

36:17.840 --> 36:18.380
Of course.

36:18.720 --> 36:19.610
Definitely.

36:21.510 --> 36:22.380
I have to.

36:35.670 --> 36:36.170
After you.

36:37.150 --> 36:38.090
Congratulations.

36:38.110 --> 36:38.970
Thank you.

36:39.400 --> 36:39.860
After you.

36:59.800 --> 37:00.570
Lei Xiuyuan,

37:00.960 --> 37:02.220
think this through.

37:02.760 --> 37:05.130
Our offer is very generous.

37:06.070 --> 37:08.490
[Luo Chengji, Lantian Sect]
If you join the Lantian Sect,

37:08.960 --> 37:11.530
we guarantee your cultivation will advance rapidly.

37:12.400 --> 37:13.900
You'll become a direct disciple

37:13.920 --> 37:15.940
of the sect master within three years.

37:17.070 --> 37:17.860
What do you say?

37:37.550 --> 37:38.170
Xiuyuan.

37:42.440 --> 37:43.050
Lifei.

37:46.320 --> 37:48.090
Wuyue Court's people haven't shown up yet.

37:49.070 --> 37:50.170
Why not come to Xingzheng Hall?

37:51.280 --> 37:51.900
It's fine.

37:52.070 --> 37:53.010
I'll wait for Wuyue Court.

37:55.400 --> 37:56.170
Your Highness!

38:10.990 --> 38:13.220
If you two join my sect,

38:13.590 --> 38:15.780
you'll surely accomplish great things.

38:16.880 --> 38:18.610
I see rare talent in you.

38:19.150 --> 38:20.260
If you join my sect

38:20.720 --> 38:22.130
and practice

38:22.760 --> 38:23.820
our techniques diligently,

38:24.360 --> 38:25.740
your power

38:26.760 --> 38:28.420
will increase significantly in no time.

38:58.720 --> 38:59.450
Mr. Shen.

38:59.590 --> 39:00.170
Mr. Zuo.

39:01.990 --> 39:04.380
You're a man of your word,

39:04.840 --> 39:07.300
coming to observe my new disciple selection.

39:08.670 --> 39:11.050
My daughter was once a master here.

39:11.470 --> 39:12.900
Of course the Wanxian Sect had to come.

39:18.990 --> 39:20.650
You're Jiang Lifei, right?

39:23.320 --> 39:24.490
Jiao mentioned you.

39:25.840 --> 39:28.130
Would you like to join Wanxian Sect?

39:31.240 --> 39:32.970
Jiao is beautiful and impressive.

39:33.150 --> 39:34.860
Of course I'd be happy to join.

39:35.760 --> 39:36.420
But

39:36.720 --> 39:38.900
for personal reasons,

39:39.110 --> 39:40.420
I have to enter Wuyue Court.

39:41.110 --> 39:42.340
Wuyue Court?

39:46.360 --> 39:46.940
By the way,

39:47.400 --> 39:49.860
if those old men at Wuyue Court don't take you,

39:50.400 --> 39:51.900
Wanxian Sect will always welcome you.

39:53.510 --> 39:54.490
Thank you, Mr. Shen.

39:55.280 --> 39:56.010
Mr. Shen,

39:56.240 --> 39:57.090
please go inside for tea.

40:04.840 --> 40:05.740
Wuyue Court's people are here!

40:07.920 --> 40:08.420
Let's go.

40:08.920 --> 40:09.650
Let's go take a look.

40:13.080 --> 40:14.920
[Wuyue Court]

40:33.800 --> 40:35.320
[Guangwei, Wuyue Court]

40:41.630 --> 40:43.740
I'm Jiang Lifei. I plead to seek entry into Wuyue Court!

40:52.960 --> 40:54.130
You're not much of a talent.

40:54.720 --> 40:56.860
Wuyue Court is not for you.

41:04.800 --> 41:06.450
I'm Lei Xiuyuan. Greetings.

41:08.590 --> 41:09.420
Lei Xiuyuan,

41:10.240 --> 41:13.860
your Metal Spirit Root is unusually rigid and unyielding.

41:14.550 --> 41:16.820
Xingzheng Hall's techniques are mostly domineering

41:17.510 --> 41:19.650
and would suit you better.

41:20.670 --> 41:22.170
But the way of the world dictates

41:22.190 --> 41:23.610
that the rigid breaks first.

41:24.990 --> 41:27.970
Sects like Dizang and Lantian aren't worth mentioning.

41:28.440 --> 41:30.450
Only Wuyue Court's techniques

41:30.920 --> 41:33.650
balance rigidity with flexibility. And that is what lasts.

41:34.990 --> 41:36.860
Would you like to join Wuyue Court?

41:37.760 --> 41:38.450
Yes.

41:44.800 --> 41:45.420
But

41:46.960 --> 41:48.130
I want to bring Jiang Lifei with me.

41:53.360 --> 41:54.090
Jiang Lifei.

41:55.800 --> 41:57.340
What sets you apart?

42:01.960 --> 42:02.860
I'm hardworking,

42:04.030 --> 42:04.940
sharp,

42:05.280 --> 42:06.010
quick-witted,

42:06.880 --> 42:08.260
respectful and caring, and resilient!

42:18.030 --> 42:18.900
I also have

42:18.920 --> 42:20.610
evil-warding beads from Immortal Dongyang.

42:22.590 --> 42:23.700
And this jade cicada from Qin.

42:35.360 --> 42:37.090
I despise nepotism more than anything.

42:37.760 --> 42:39.220
Wuyue Court will not take you!

42:42.200 --> 42:43.200
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:43.200 --> 42:44.720
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:55.800 --> 42:59.480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

42:59.800 --> 43:02.480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

43:02.560 --> 43:05.800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

43:05.800 --> 43:09.080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

43:09.200 --> 43:13.080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

43:13.360 --> 43:16.560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

43:16.720 --> 43:22.800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

43:23.080 --> 43:27.200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

43:27.480 --> 43:30.160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

43:30.360 --> 43:32.280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

43:32.400 --> 43:36.720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

43:36.880 --> 43:40.720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

43:41.080 --> 43:44.080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

43:44.160 --> 43:50.280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

43:50.480 --> 43:54.200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

44:07.440 --> 44:11.200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

44:11.400 --> 44:14.200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

44:14.280 --> 44:17.680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

44:17.680 --> 44:21.000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

44:21.160 --> 44:25.000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

44:25.160 --> 44:28.360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

44:28.600 --> 44:34.440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

44:35.000 --> 44:38.920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

44:39.200 --> 44:41.960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

44:42.160 --> 44:44.000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

44:44.160 --> 44:48.360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

44:48.600 --> 44:52.480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

44:52.720 --> 44:55.760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

44:55.960 --> 45:02.680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

45:02.720 --> 45:06.680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

45:06.920 --> 45:09.680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

45:09.800 --> 45:11.720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

45:11.880 --> 45:16.160
♪Break through the waves; the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

45:16.360 --> 45:20.200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

45:20.440 --> 45:23.560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

45:23.600 --> 45:29.600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water♪

45:30.000 --> 45:34.360
♪And falling petals♪
